Apprenez en mobilité sur cette espace accessible via vos login et mot de passe de l’Académie by Intersport. Partagez, likez, commentez et interagissez avec vos communautés.
descriptionShort: Find all your training in your pocket.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Path assessments can now be validated/rejected on mobile devices
- Improved the language selection on courses
- We have also deployed fixes and improvements as per your feedback
